{"tid":893016,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"吳亦凡遭美國 ITunes 刪除銷售數據　銷量榜冠軍被指造假　","createTime":"2018-11-07T09:53:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-07T11:49:51.000Z","uid":69038,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e32eaf1fefd4fed439ab2c7297df39bb0b9503f0","tid":893016,"uid":69038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T09:53:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/11/07/kris-wu/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F11%2F07%2Fkris-wu%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=VSeDE8ZXGasK5mTbQXGUx%2FjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=a1a30e0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/11/07/kris-wu/fun-tech/</a><br />\n<br />\n韓國男團 EXO 的前中國成員吳亦凡，於本月 2 日推出了首張個人大碟 《Antares》，在美國 iTunes 的銷量榜上名列前矛，更一度力壓 Ariana Grande 及 Lady Gaga 等天后級歌手，引發大批網民關注。其後，有傳言指吳亦凡新專輯的成績，是透過大量支持者不斷重覆購買來推高成績。<br />\n<br />\n美國方面的 iTunes 在調查事件後，直接將吳亦凡新歌的數據清除。 Lady Gaga 及 Ariana Grande 重回銷量榜冠軍及亞軍地位。Ariana Grande 的經理人被指發文投訴吳亦凡使用作弊手段推高銷量成績，但他其後於 Twitter 上發文否認有關言論。有傳 Ariana Grande 也讚好了諷刺吳亦凡的貼文，甚有火藥味。<br />\n<br />\n據《網易》報道，吳亦凡支持者事前經過多月準備，當專輯正式推出後，就不斷切換帳號重覆購買。務求做出最驚人的成績。但現時 Apple 方面已刪去新專輯所有銷售數據了。"},{"pid":"9dc227ed313ce4299a6ca7058f706af227e1236c","tid":893016,"uid":56957,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T09:58:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/18/195803_f300be837024fa3a925cd6efa17a1967.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F18%2F195803_f300be837024fa3a925cd6efa17a1967.png&h=63a48d43&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"84aa8692d75d8d1c3dd21954568fbf49f0b416b9","tid":893016,"uid":82482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T09:59:01.000Z","msg":"who?"},{"pid":"f6955d01496af058dea59ff71cc4f5a6299c5187","tid":893016,"uid":69484,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T10:00:17.000Z","msg":"老實講 佢係好紅 <br />\n大陸明星淨係識佢"},{"pid":"2e6b9e101a170e26e6fe8991576be6c3e9b7ee